{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_05_03",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 3話 記憶を胸に",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、すみません\nここまで付き合ってもらっちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I'm sorry.\nThank you for coming this far with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 6.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "明日のリズノワのライブで、お姉ちゃんの曲を歌う……\nそう思ったら、少しでも星見市の景色を眺めたくなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomorrow‚ during LizNoir's live performance‚ I'll be singing my sister's song…\nWhen I thought about that‚ I wanted to gaze at the scenery of Hoshimi City even just a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "気合いを入れるため、という訳か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To get yourself pumped up‚ I assume?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 20.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん。私、明日お姉ちゃんの曲を歌うけど……\nお手柔らかにね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Big sis‚ tomorrow I'll be singing your song‚\nbut please go easy on me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 29.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんがいなくなった時の、悲しさとか\n感情をぶつける相手がいなくなったもどかしさとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The intense emotions‚ like the sadness when big sis disappeared‚\nand the frustration of not having someone to express those feelings to…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そういう激しい感情は薄れてきたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Those intense emotions have started to fade away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "それに、アイドル活動を続ける中で考えることも\nだいぶ変わってきたなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ the things I think about have changed\nquite a bit in the midst of my idol activities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "星見市にいた頃は、「こんな時、お姉ちゃんなら\nどうするんだろう？」って何度も考えてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was in Hoshimi City‚ I used to think‚\n\"What would big sis do in times like these?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "でも今は、少しずつ自分の足で立って、アイドルとして\n進めるようになってきた気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ I feel like I can stand on my own two feet\nlittle by little and progress as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 64.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃はもう、立派なアイドルだよ。俺が保証する",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ you've become a splendid idol. I guarantee it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 71.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、初めの頃に{user}さんに同じ\nようなことを言われても信じられなかったでしょうけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure when I first met {user}-san‚\nI wouldn't have believed if someone said the same thing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "出会った頃は本当に信用されてなかったな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back when we first met‚ I really wasn't trusted…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 82.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "今はちゃんと頼りにしてますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ I rely on you with confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "自分の足で進んで、月ストや星見のみんな……そして\n{user}さんを信頼するようになって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've gradually gained the ability to stand on my own in the idol world‚\nand I've started to believe in Moon Tempest‚ the people in Hoshimi‚ and also in {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとずつ、お姉ちゃん離れ出来てる気がするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm starting to become a bit more",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それって嬉しくもあるんですけど……\n少しだけ、寂しいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "independent from my big sister.\nBut‚ it's also a little lonely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "だんだん忙しくなって、お姉ちゃんのことを考える\n時間も減って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gradually‚ as things got busier‚ I found myself thinking about big sis…\nMy time became scarce…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "いつどこにいても、お姉ちゃんのことで\n頭が一杯だったあの頃の私とは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wherever I was‚ my mind was filled with thoughts of big sis…\nThat me from back then‚ who was consumed by thoughts of my sister‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 119.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんがいなくなった頃の私とは\nもう違うんだなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and the me from when big sis was no longer here…\nI'm different now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 125.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "悲しみで立ち上がることさえ出来なかった\nあの頃に戻りたい訳じゃないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I couldn't even muster the strength to stand up from sadness back then.\nIt's not that I want to go back to those times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、なんだか……私の中で、お姉ちゃんが\n遠くに行ってしまう気がして、寂しいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But still‚ in some way…\nI feel like big sis is slipping away‚ and it's lonely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "その気持ちは……分かるよ。悲しみと一緒に\n思い出まで薄れてしまいそうになるんだよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that feeling. Along with the sadness‚\nthe memories seem like they're fading away too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_03-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "だから私は、お姉ちゃんの曲を歌いたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I want to sing big sis's song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 154.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
